About Me

Who Am I?

Hello, I am Donghyun Park and I am currently a rising senior at The Cooper Union majoring in Electrical Computer Engineering. I expect to graduate in the Spring (May) of 2021.

I created this website as a showcase for my personal and academic projects, as well as gain more experience in full stack developing.
The more I learn, the more I realize the depth of what I still have yet to learn, and that amount of potential I see excites me!
